com.infostretch.automation.util

Annotation Type Randomizer


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=FIELD)
public @interface Randomizer
    This annotation can be used with BaseDataBean properties. It will be used by BaseDataBean.fillRandomData() method.
